Bitcoin Accountability Pacts
Bitcoin Logo
"Enforce personal promises with Bitcoin Script - break them, burn sats."

🏆 MIT Bitcoin Hackathon 2025 Submission
Demo: https://bitcoinpacts.carrd.co/ | Video Walkthrough: https://youtu.be/_7LOd4dMOU0?si=j157f4wQANJuCxvU

🚀 Key Innovation
First behavioral accountability system using:
✔ Native Bitcoin Script (no altcoins/smart contracts)
✔ Loss aversion psychology (sat burning for failure)
✔ Censorship-resistant promises (OP_RETURN/covenants) 

 Why Bitcoin?

"Traditional commitment apps (e.g., StickK) require trust in centralized entities. Bitcoin Pacts make accountability trustless and immutable."

🛠️ Technical Implementation
Core Components
Component	        Implementation Details
Promise Engine	  PSBTs with CLTV/CSV time locks
Data Storage	    OP_RETURN (testnet) → Taproot covenants (mainnet-ready)
Failure Penalty	   Pre-signed tx burning pledged UTXO
Frontend	         Carrd.co + Google Forms PSBT generator


                            
